{"tid":2329720,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"WeLab Bank 藍定黃？Ben Sir 介紹唔一定係黃","createTime":"2020-12-17T12:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T15:44:02.000Z","uid":381081,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cad7ce9d6608d246e156ae97431e0c25936bf6a2","tid":2329720,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pGxuBu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpGxuBu9.jpg&h=68e58084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">WeLab Bank 藍定黃？Ben Sir 介紹唔一定係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\nShare link:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109544990929806/posts/139468757937429/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109544990929806%2Fposts%2F139468757937429%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28Y6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=ff4df7ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109544990929806/posts/139468757937429/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n👉大家幫手share，以防同路人資產被凍結👈<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日不能睇電視、YT 同 FB 都見到佢哋嘅廣告，但有唔少網民留言質疑WeLab背景。 <br />\n<br />\n亦有人認為Ben Sir 介紹得一個咁「本土」嘅 #虛擬銀行，唔多唔少都係黃（？）<br />\n<br />\n但睇真啲，唔單止公司嘅CEO 現職多個政府核下委員會<br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳仲曾經做過深圳市消委會委員！<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇公司背後嘅投資者：<br />\n🇨🇳阿里巴巴（如果咁都信得過，不如大家用返支付寶）<br />\n🇨🇳中國建設銀行（嫌匯豐凍結得太慢？☃️）<br />\n🇨🇳TOM 集團（背後同多個共產黨擁有國企緊密合作 eg.中國郵政）<br />\n<br />\n而事實上，香港市面所有虛擬銀行，都係有中資背景公司參與，所以大家可以死咗條心<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以參考：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/106471067808095/posts/116945220094013/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F106471067808095%2Fposts%2F116945220094013%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28Y6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=7888676a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/106471067808095/posts/116945220094013/?d=n</a>  和你 FC<br />\n<br />\n支持我們開發App、推廣黃圈👉 <a